    <item>
      <title>强劲的经济将医疗保险基金的生存能力延长至 2036 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/medicare-insurance-fund-outlook-improves-on-stronger-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据财政部周一发布的一份报告，医疗保险的医院保险信托基金将能够在 2036 年之前支付全额福利，比一年前的预测晚了五年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/medicare-insurance-fund-outlook-improves-on-stronger-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场货币延续今年最大幅度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/emerging-market-trio-gets-credit-rating-boost-as-rally-extends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币延续了 2024 年最大的四天涨幅，交易员谨慎地提高了对美联储今年降息的押注，刺激了对风险资产的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/emerging-market-trio-gets-credit-rating-boost-as-rally-extends</guid>
